    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Lighthouse bans peers when their score drops below a certain level\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/stable/beacon_node/eth2_libp2p/src/peer_manager/score.rs\r\n\r\nOnce that happens it will block connections for some time, potentially long. However, we keep trying to connect to peers that have banned us very often, sometimes every 30 seconds.\r\n\r\nSo we def have to investigate why we are banned, but it may be just 4 peers that are constantly sending a goodbye \"banned\" code.",
